OL,3,C'Take 5 Seconds': NSPCC offering
OL,4,Csupport to parents to help them stay
OL,5,Ccalm
OL,7,FNSPCC Northern Ireland is urging
OL,8,Fparents and carers to "Take 5 Seconds"
OL,9,Fbefore acting aggressively towards
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FIt's part of a new campaign that
OL,13,Facknowledges the challenges facing
OL,14,Fparents, while also raising awareness
OL,15,Fabout the negative impact that anger
OL,16,Fcan have on young people.
