OL,3,C'Take 5 Seconds': NSPCC offering
OL,4,Csupport to parents to help them stay
OL,5,Ccalm
OL,7,FMargaret Gallagher from the NSPCC
OL,8,Fsaid: "Often parents can be very
OL,9,Fcritical of themselves or may think
OL,10,Fthat others are being judgmental when
OL,11,Fthese situations arise, maybe when the
OL,12,Fchild is having a bit of a meltdown in
OL,13,Fthe in the supermarket.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
