OL,5,Ccalm
OL,7,F"But as I say these things are normal,
OL,8,Fbabies are learning, young children
OL,9,Fare learning, they're testing
OL,10,Fboundaries, and just if you take that
OL,11,Ftime and you find your calm, it can
OL,12,Fhelp manage the situation and bring
OL,13,Fthat connectedness with you and your
OL,14,Fchild."
OL,16,FResearch carried out by the charity
OL,17,Fsuggests just 33% of parents in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland have received
OL,19,Finformation about positive parenting.
