OL,3,C'Take 5 Seconds': NSPCC offering
OL,4,Csupport to parents to help them stay
OL,5,Ccalm
OL,7,FAs a result, it has put together some
OL,8,Fadvice and support that's available on
OL,9,Ftheir website to help people to stay
OL,10,Fcalm during challenging moments.
OL,12,FThis includes taking a breath before
OL,13,Facting, communicating clearly with the
OL,14,Fchild, and smiling if possible.
OL,16,FThe Health Minister has backed the
OL,17,Fcampaign, and said he shares the
OL,18,Fworries and concerns many other
OL,19,Fparents experience.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
