OL,3,C'Take 5 Seconds': NSPCC offering
OL,4,Csupport to parents to help them stay
OL,5,Ccalm
OL,7,FHe said: "I don't think I've ever met
OL,8,Fa parent who doesn't want to know how
OL,9,Fto do it better, so any advice, any
OL,10,Fprogrammes like 'Take 5 Seconds' are
OL,11,Falways going to be welcome.
OL,13,F"This initiative is all about how you
OL,14,Fmediate and control your emotions so
OL,15,Fthat they don't impact negatively on
OL,16,Fthe emotions of a child so it's about
OL,17,Fregulating how you feel, and being
OL,18,Fable to take a step back."
OL,20,FMore information on the campaign can
OL,21,Fbe found here.
